<button type="button" class="help-button btn btn-success" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#slackHelpModal">
  Help &amp; How To
</button>

<div class="modal fade" id="slackHelpModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="slackHelpModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="slackHelpModalLabel">Help &amp; How To</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>During the week shoutout to people who helped you out.</p>
        <pre><strong>/shoutout</strong> <em>@person</em> saved me a ton of time with all the things. Thanks!</pre>

        <p>Made a mistake? Change the course of history with:</p>
        <pre><strong>/shoutout</strong> undo</pre>

        <p>At the end of the week take a look at all the shoutouts on this page and cheer on 3 favorites. Click the buttons on this page to build the <code>/cheer</code> command. It should to look something like this:</p>
        <pre><strong>/cheer</strong> #1 #2 #3</pre>

        <p>Made another mistake? You can <code>undo</code> the latest cheer and <code>clear</code> all cheers like this:</p>
        <pre><strong>/cheer</strong> undo</pre>
        <pre><strong>/cheer</strong> clear</pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="slackCommandModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="slackCommandModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="slackCommandModalLabel">Cheer Command</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Copy and paste the below command into Slack</p>
        <input readonly type="text" class="form-control" id="commandBox" placeholder="/cheer ...">
        <div id="mobileCommandBox"></div>
        <button type="button" class="clear-cheers btn btn-danger" data-dismiss="modal">Dismiss and Start Over</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<header>
  <h1 class="title text-center">Three Cheers</h1>
  <p class="subtitle text-center">hip hip hooray!</p>
  <% unless @shoutouts.empty? %>
    <p class="text-center">
      <strong><%= @shoutouts.size %></strong> shoutouts
      sent from <strong><%= unique_senders_count(@shoutouts) %></strong>
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>
      to
      <strong><%= unique_recipients_count(@shoutouts) %></strong>
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>
      this week.
      <% if (count = cheer_count(@shoutouts)) > 0 %>
        <%= count %> ðŸŽ‰
      <% end %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <div class="shoutouts">
    <hr>
    <% if @shoutouts.empty? %>
      <p class="text-center">All is quiet</p>
    <% end %>
    <% @shoutouts.each do |s| %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-1">
          <p class="lead shoutout-id">#<%= s.id %> <span class="timestamp"><%= time_ago_message(s.created_at) %></span></p>
            <button class="cheer-button btn btn-default" type="submit" id="<%= s.id %>">ðŸŽ‰</button>
            <span class="cheer-button-counter" id="b<%= s.id %>"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-11">
          <p>
            <strong><%= s.sender %></strong> made a shoutout to
            <%= format_recipients(s.recipients).html_safe %>
          </p>
          <div class="cheer well">
            <p class="lead"><%= highlight_usernames(s.message, s.recipients).html_safe %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr>
    <% end %>
    <p class="the-end text-center">
      the end...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
      <a href="https://trello.com/b/lTJyK69o/cheers">Feedback</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
